    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Historicist architecture style developed from the latter 19th century and onwards. Adopts neoclassical ornamentation from the Louis XVI period (1774-1792), such as oval medallions, laurel and fasces motifs.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
